room_title: Escape room "M.A.S.K." by Puzzah! in Santa Fe
room_description: INTERCEPT is threatening the city with acts of cyberterrorism. An elite crime-fighting team called M.A.S.K. has formed to respond to the INTERCEPT threat. M.A.S.K. needs heroes like you with the skills to infiltrate enemy bases and defeat hostile agents. Will you answer the call and join the M.A.S.K. team?
